# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Data files — excluded from version control.
# Raw inputs and all generated CSV/Excel outputs are NOT tracked in git.
# They are either:
#   - auto-downloaded by the pipeline scripts (e.g. eer.csv, S&P 500), or
#   - regenerated by running the pipeline (process_fed_shocks.py,
#     prepare_reer_controls.py, run_lp_*.py, fed_dva_analysis/scripts/*.py).
# See README.md §3 for the end-to-end reproduction pipeline.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.parquet
*.feather
*.dta
*.sav
*.rds
data_raw/
